    <!-- Refresh Mode Descriptions -->
    <string name="always_on_desc">In this mode updates of the displayed information happen smoothly. The screen light might have to be turned to the \'cold\' color temperature for the light to turn off.</string>
    <string name="battery_saver_desc">In this mode the phone sleeps between updates to save as much power as possible. Depending on your screen lock it might require pin entry.</string>
    <string name="hybrid_desc">In this mode the \'Always On\' mode is used initially, and if the phone has not been used for over 2 hours it switches to \'Battery Saver\' mode.</string>
    <string name="deep_sleep_desc">In this mode the \'Always On\' mode is used initially, and if the phone has not been used for over 2 hours it goes to sleep and only shows a static image, drawing no extra power.</string>
    
